{"tid":1456943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地係一家人黎","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:13.000Z","uid":175748,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f782f37911640cab4efb92bab0014cd07e43e6","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:03:14.000Z","msg":"人地出一場鬼就令我地互不信任<br />\n一日就差唔多打散我地<br />\n我覺得今日叫人走既未必係鬼<br />\n係因為對班狗既不信任，特別係琴晚，佢地有底線咩？<br />\n大家只係擔心唔想手足受傷，真係唔想再流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場決定的確係最好，但係又時真係太多人<br />\n資訊未必傳達到比咁多人聽<br />\n<br />\n明白大家都好嬲好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係大家唔好忘記我地兩個月而黎既團結<br />\n先可以行到今日，我敢講我生為香港人已經無悔<br />\n大家唔好再話人係鬼/分化啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地係一家人黎<br />\n唔好內部分裂</span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，決一不可<br />\n不受傷，不流血，不被捕<br />\n不分化，不割席，不認輸<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"f20129fb603643d8a8a3858544dcb2b579431226","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:07:16.000Z","msg":"推團結post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ce003dd3f3c0da688c2ff7cc27945ef35cc1e4","tid":1456943,"uid":231124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"無論鐘意散保命也好，鍾意堅持原則留守也好，大家出得嚟嘅都係兄弟，今日唔得咪下一次再嚟囉，兄弟爬山，不分化，不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898f9404e8a261da1459aee2321eb1a6662b55f3","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n人地出左一招渣<br />\n大家頂住呀"},{"pid":"ef0506962241956563cfc050759eda503c9de815","tid":1456943,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:18:42.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e8737cfa7a4f04c7a61f90cd95654615d1287069","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c593919142866dc8d98c1278e2da60a8380806f0","tid":1456943,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"推，走唔走都唔會立即成功/失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果冇走，佢可能真係圍捕<br />\n如果走晒，可能佢會復飛<br />\n<br />\n所以冇絕對對錯，不分化為大原則矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc912751bd1cc96e930eebd8059635ab0936eb9","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"唔同意都可以入黎屌我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03c0505862b2ad31cd2d882720a124ab73d014b","tid":1456943,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"5a1f6247c56986d3cb9c0c6241ee181bbcae4690","tid":1456943,"uid":194553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"係呀 撤定留大家都有各自既理由 唔好指責另一方"},{"pid":"bb9ca8b6601370879de1908a1410e4cd57899513","tid":1456943,"uid":139237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"屌散水跟本冇負過責任<br />\n最重要大家都睇到現場有鬼係事實<br />\n點解仲要手足冒險（可能又有人話以後有鬼就以後唔駛倏）<br />\n短短一日都未夠時間都未商討好點應對[鬼]<br />\n萬一出左事，點對得住犧牲既手足<br />\n如果有人可以100%確保安全先有絕對資格叫人留，每一個人都會自我風險評估<br />\n跟本麻木屌任何一方都唔會有得著"},{"pid":"c33bf290cc12a70794c09df5df68005333b1988e","tid":1456943,"uid":287582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:51.000Z","msg":"我認錯  <br />\n我只係想大家都安全 <br />\n要屌我就儘力屌啦  <br />\n屌完就再諗方法<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不切割 兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"1389bee46e2cd7e1d7db75701c85b1284420f3b6","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />追究警黑勾結"},{"pid":"8c1d7ccd514f4ceec597cf56fa5241093e650eb2","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a138be39c7eea95e1d8f2169c55334536a9674","tid":1456943,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ad5ae0af7145c3c3278fde9d71d69e78961672","tid":1456943,"uid":98826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8884c677d26d96e3a27b7c3317c2169afdda76af","tid":1456943,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:11:37.000Z","msg":"不要說推，請說<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，近距離開槍射擊<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警犬在太古站推人落電梯<br />\n7. 荃灣攻擊平民"},{"pid":"62dc09c55c776246f4a298c2882c18e762f3a816","tid":1456943,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3e27z53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3e27z53.jpg&h=e6198eac&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}